Fluxus : (C) 2005 Dave Griffiths : dave at pawfal dot org : www.pawfal.org

act of a flowing; a continuous moving on or passing by, as of a flowing stream; a continuous 
succession of changes

fluxus is a small realtime render engine for linux that generates animation from sound.
released under the GPL licence (see COPYING)

see INSTALL for information on building

contents

doc/index.html : documentation on the application and scripting language
examples/      : a loose collection of example scripts, tests and live scripts I've used
scm/           : a set of util scheme code for various tasks (not much here yet)
textures/      : some textures used in the examples

